snippet.title: #LegendOfTheDoubleDragon - Supreme Demonstration
snippet.description:
UltimateDoubleDragon_Q: https://discord.gg/wQ46pBwsGT

Get the demo & please support the cause by donating on the official website where you can also get the LEGEND OF THE DOUBLE DRAGON (ver 1.5) and learn about this ULTIMATE DOUBLE DRAGON project at:
www.openborgx.wordpress.com

Follow me on Twitter for quick dev news about UDD at:
https://twitter.com/ToffyHC

Follow mr. Koji Ogata's Twitter for lots of OG Double Dragon & Kunio Kun series content at:
https://twitter.com/food2han

Check Ogata-san sites for more of his old days Technos goodies at:
https://ogata1.wixsite.com/works1
https://www.zazzle.co.jp/store/doubledragon_kunio

Follow my brother Patricio Herrera's YT channel for all kind of awesome remixes at:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCoAt4icZXiytDvbcehvCcMg

Follow Krauser's channel about all kinds of music & the Ultimate Double Dragon Retrosynth Soundtrack at:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC2SS33cOUmc8VzRSQbZQhZQ
